data.description:
JUST REDUCED!! NEW 14 SEER A/C purchased summer 2022. YOU WILL LOVE this generous roomy floor plan!! Bedrooms are all good size, Family room is HUGE with enough room for a long dining room table. Brand new Frigidaire electric stove w/air fryer inside. NEW TUFF SHED (10x12fr + 8ft high) to keep you organized with extra  extra storage. Programmable thermostat you can set to your phone. Backyard is inviting with covered patio for relaxing and gatherings all year round! Lots of fruit trees and garden beds of vegetables. Also NEW Kinetico Water System throughout home. 
Please use SHOWING TIME!!!
 ITEMS THAT DO NOT CONVEY: Refrigerator, Freezer, Washer, Dryer, Trampoline, Umbrellas, Bird Bath 
 & Swing on patio.
